subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: C.J. McCollum scored 30 points and Lehigh upset Duke to become the second No. 15 seed to beat a No. 2, after Norfolk State performed the feat earlier in the day.
